      resp←''
      :Trap 0 DebugLevel 1
          :Trap 85
     stop1:   resp←{1 CodeLocation.(85⌶)exec,' ⍵'}ns.Req  ⍝ intentional stop for application-level debugging
          :EndTrap
          ⍬ ⎕STOP⊃⎕SI
      :Else
          ⍬ ⎕STOP⊃⎕SI
          →0⊣ns.Req.Fail 500
      :EndTrap
      →0 If 2≠⌊0.01×ns.Req.Response.Status
      :If (ns.Req.(Response.Headers GetHeader'content-type')≡'')∧~0∊⍴DefaultContentType
